text: "Collide" is a single by American hip-hop and R&B; singer Justine Skye, released on August 25, 2014.https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/collide- feat.-tyga-single/id910758596 The track features a guest verse by American rapper Tyga and was produced by DJ Mustard. ==Music video== A music video for the single featuring Tyga, was released on Justine's YouTube channel, on October 8, 2014 and has today over 2 million views. ==Chart performance== {| class="wikitable sortable plainrowheaders" |- !
